.section 'The Output Device and the Formatting Environment'
..pp;SYSPUB assumes that the formatted document is to be produced on
..ix 2 'page layout' 'dimensions'
..ix 2 'page layout' 'left and right margins'
8.5x11 pages with a 1.5-inch margin on the left and 1-inch margins on th
top, bottom, and right.
If the output device is a high-speed line printer, no special
..ix 2 'page layout' printer
printer setup is necessary (aside from white paper and an upper- and
lower-case print train).  If the output device is a typewriter terminal,
..ix 2 'page layout' typewriter
the left margin of the typewriter should be set one-half inch in from
the left side of the paper.
..pp;If you want the text of the publication to be double-spaced, specif
..ix 2 'double-spacing'
the SCRIPT ".ds" control word
..us before ×you imbed SYSPUB.
